---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - TheBestOffersAround.com">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="mb-8">About TheBestOffersAround.com</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-gray-300">
      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          At TheBestOffersAround.com, our mission is simple: to help you discover the best products, 
          courses, and tools that can genuinely improve your life. We carefully curate and review 
          each offer to ensure it provides real value.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">What We Do</h2>
        <p>
          We specialize in finding high-quality products across multiple categories including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>Health & Fitness programs</li>
          <li>Digital Marketing courses and tools</li>
          <li>Make Money Online systems</li>
          <li>Self-Improvement resources</li>
          <li>Software & Productivity tools</li>
          <li>Educational eBooks & Courses</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Our Process</h2>
        <p>
          Every product featured on our site goes through a rigorous evaluation process:
        </p>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>We research products from reputable marketplaces</li>
          <li>We verify the credibility of the product creator</li>
          <li>We analyze customer reviews and feedback</li>
          <li>We negotiate exclusive discounts when possible</li>
          <li>We present our findings with complete transparency</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Transparency & Trust</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in complete transparency. As an affiliate marketing website, we earn commissions 
          when you make purchases through our links. However, this never influences our recommendations. 
          We only feature products we believe can genuinely help our audience.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Our affiliate relationships allow us to provide you with exclusive discounts and deals that 
          you might not find elsewhere, while keeping our content free for everyone.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Get In Touch</h2>
        <p>
          Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you. Visit our 
          <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact page</a> to get in touch.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
